             <!-- <span class=\"recinfos-list__area is-orange\">\n                                【札幌市西区】\n                              </span> -->\n                                                        <span class=\"recinfos-list__title\">事務職（総合事務）</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </a>\n                      </li>\n                                      </ul>\n                              </div>\n            </section>\n                      <section id=\"functional-training-instructor\" class=\"page-section anchor-target\" style=\"z-index: 1;\">\n              <header class=\"heading02 u-mb0\">\n                <h2 class=\"heading02__text\">理学療法士・柔道整復師・鍼灸師　<span class=\"is-black\">の求人</span></h2>\n              </header>\n              <div class=\"page-section__content\">\n                                  <ul class=\"recinfos-list\">\n                                          <li class=\"recinfos-list__item\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1347/\" class=\"recinfos-list__link\">\n                                                      <span class=\"recinfos-list__status\">\n                              正                            </span>\n                                                    <div class=\"recinfos-list__block\">\n                                                        <span class=\"recinfos-list__title\">理学療法士</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </a>\n                      </li>\n                                          <li class=\"recinfos-list__item\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruitment_info/1247/\" class=\"recinfos-list__link\">\n                                                      <span class=\"recinfos-list__status\">\n                              正                            </span>\n                                                    <div class=\"recinfos-list__block\">\n                                                        <span class=\"recinfos-list__title\">柔道整復師</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </a>\n                      </li>\n                                      </ul>\n                              </div>\n            </section>\n                    <section class=\"page-section\">\n            <header class=\"heading01\">\n              <h2 class=\"heading01__text\">採用の流れ</h2>\n              <div class=\"heading01__dot\">\n                <span></span>\n                <span></span>\n                <span></span>\n              </div>\n            </header>\n            <div class=\"inner\">\n              <p>応募から採用までは4つのSTEPで速やかに進みます。柔道整復師・鍼灸師の方は、採用後に講習を実施していますので、ブランクがある方でも安心してご応募いただけます。</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"box\">\n              <div class=\"inner\">\n                <ul class=\"list05\">\n                  <li class=\"list05__item\">\n                    <div class=\"list05__wrap\">\n                      <div class=\"list05__head\">\n                        <div class=\"list05__ribon\">\n                          <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/ribon_entry_step01.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"list05__heading\">応 募</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"list05__content\">\n                        <p>\n                          <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit/entry/\">エントリーフォーム</a> からご応募ください。<br>\n                          ご不明点はお電話いただいても大丈夫です。\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"list05__item\">\n                    <div class=\"list05__wrap\">\n                      <div class=\"list05__head\">\n                        <div class=\"list05__ribon\">\n                          <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/ribon_entry_step02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"list05__heading\">面 接</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"list05__content\">\n                        <p>\n                          面接官とのお話と筆記試験（SPI適性検査）。<br>\n                          リラックスして来てくださいね！\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"list05__item\">\n                    <div class=\"list05__wrap\">\n                      <div class=\"list05__head\">\n                        <div class=\"list05__ribon\">\n                          <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/ribon_entry_step03.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"list05__heading\">施設見学</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"list05__content\">\n                        <p>\n                          面接が終わったら、応募職種のスタッフを見学。職場の雰囲気がわかります。\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"list05__item\">\n                    <div class=\"list05__wrap\">\n                      <div class=\"list05__head\">\n                        <div class=\"list05__ribon\">\n                          <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/ribon_entry_step04.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"list05__heading\">採用結果</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"list05__content\">\n                        <p>\n                          面接から1週間以内に電話でご連絡。合否に関わらず、必ずご連絡させていただきます。\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"list05__item\">\n                    <div class=\"list05__wrap\">\n                      <div class=\"list05__head\">\n                        <div class=\"list05__ribon\">\n                          <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/ribon_entry_step05.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"list05__heading\">導入前講習</p>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"list05__content\">\n                        <p>\n                          柔道整復師・鍼灸師は実践に向けた講習あり。<br>\n                          スムーズに業務を始められます。\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </section>\n          <div id=\"entry\" class=\"anchor-target\">\n  <div  class=\"entry-box\">\n    <!-- <img src=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/wp-content/themes/magokoro-theme/images/recruit/top/top_text_Joinus.png\" class=\"rectop-txt\"> -->\n    <p>まごころで、<br class=\"hide-pc\">一緒に働いてみませんか。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.magokorosapporo.com/recruit/\">採用トップへ</a>\n  </div>\n</div>        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <header class=\"heading u-center\">\n          <p class=\"heading__subtext u-fonten\">CONTACT</p>\n          <h2 class=\"heading__text\">お問い合わせ</h2>\n        </header>\n        <p class=\"u-pc-center\">\n          デイサービスのことや自宅介護の始め方など、お役に立てることがあれば<br class=\"sp-hide\">ぜひご相談ください。まごころがお手伝いさせていただきます。\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"contact-content\">\n          <p class=\"contact-text is-orange\">お気軽にお問い合わせください</p>\n          <div class=\"contact-btns\">\n            <div class=\"sp-hide\">\n              <span class=\"contact-btn contact-btn--tel\">\n                <span class=\"u-fonten\">011-613-3579</span>\n                <span>（ 代表 ）</span>\n 